data.description: This beautiful three bedroom two and a half bathroom home in Brentwood Terrace features just over two thousand square feet all on one level. The house sits back nicely from the road and has a long driveway capable of accommodating multiple vehicles. Inside you'll see a fantastic and large living space with an iconic midcentury wood burning fireplace as the focal point. Head through the kitchen and find a second living area with a view to the back yard through the newer sliding glass door off of the office. Just outside the door is a newly poured concrete patio creating an inviting outdoor space in the big back yard. This home has so much great space and style to offer you won't want to miss it! Call to schedule your private showing today.
